Interface DoubleStreamDecorator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.util.stream.BaseStream<java.lang.Double,java.util.stream.DoubleStream>, BaseStreamDecorator<java.lang.Double,java.util.stream.DoubleStream>, java.util.stream.DoubleStream
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceStream.DoubleResourceStream

    public interface DoubleStreamDecorator
extends BaseStreamDecorator<java.lang.Double,java.util.stream.DoubleStream>, java.util.stream.DoubleStream
    A decorator for a DoubleStream which wraps intermediate and terminal operations such that they can be easily extended.
